WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.773 --> 00:00:03.840
Welcome and good evening, family.

00:00:03.840 --> 00:00:06.160
Thank you for joining me again tonight.

00:00:06.160 --> 00:00:19.640
I'm going to go over some of the things that the Lord showed us in our last prayer video, and I'll go over some things that are new today that I've gotten over the last 24 hours praying with the Lord.

00:00:25.040 --> 00:00:29.093
Holy Spirit, I invite you in this time of prayer.

00:00:29.502 --> 00:00:34.720
I thank you, Lord, that it is uninterrupted and unhindered by any satanic or demonic force.

00:00:34.720 --> 00:00:37.940
Father, I ask you to pray through me.

00:00:38.440 --> 00:00:42.080
Holy Spirit, I ask you to speak through my vocal cords and think through my mind.

00:00:42.080 --> 00:00:45.679
None of me and all of you, in Jesus' name.

00:00:45.679 --> 00:00:46.079
Amen.

00:00:46.879 --> 00:00:52.800
Holy Spirit, we invite Him and we're so thankful for Him.

00:00:52.800 --> 00:00:57.640
I think the last prayer video was probably one of my favorites of the year so far.

00:00:57.640 --> 00:01:03.440
I don't know how many people watched that, but it truly blessed me.

00:01:03.931 --> 00:01:16.944
Everything the Lord showed me about the revival with John Kilpatrick and the churches around America with Perry Stone—I've just been meditating on it, soaking it in.

00:01:18.480 --> 00:01:30.000
We can go from one place to another and just take for granted what God has done through this channel and what He's showing us so gracefully.

00:01:30.000 --> 00:01:41.360
Or you can take the moment to pause and just really breathe in that fragrance of who He is and what He's about to do in this earth.

00:01:41.360 --> 00:01:42.347
It's amazing.

00:01:42.676 --> 00:01:48.114
I don't want to take for granted those times; they're precious to me.

00:01:48.114 --> 00:01:55.892
Diana and I have been meditating, running those things through our minds and thinking about what God said about Pastor John Kilpatrick.

00:02:01.280 --> 00:02:12.053
I don't even know them or their church, but I've watched some of the online services to catch up with some of the things he's saying.

00:02:12.520 --> 00:02:15.337
They're a hungry church.

00:02:15.337 --> 00:02:24.300
He had a sermon series in his archives; I listened to two of them and they really blessed me.

00:02:24.300 --> 00:02:27.767
I was trying to think of what it was called, but it was phenomenal.

00:02:33.017 --> 00:02:33.291
He preaches amazingly.

00:02:34.062 --> 00:02:36.996
I encourage you all to listen to it.

00:02:45.960 --> 00:02:51.840
We've listened to a bunch of them now because I wanted to know if we're right.

00:02:52.377 --> 00:02:59.059
Whenever you're hearing in the spirit and the Lord's showing you things, you don't want to be flaky.

00:03:01.519 --> 00:03:05.429
I don't want to be a part of the flakiness; I want to flow with the Holy Spirit.

00:03:05.599 --> 00:03:06.399
If it's off, it's off.

00:03:06.933 --> 00:03:08.995
I'm not here to make excuses.

00:03:08.995 --> 00:03:12.541
If I miss it, I miss it, but I want to be quick to tell you.

00:03:15.706 --> 00:03:20.491
The Lord is telling me that He's going to renew his veins and his arteries, renewing his body like the eagles.

00:03:26.440 --> 00:03:27.370
The glory of the Lord is coming on John Kilpatrick like Moses.

00:03:33.154 --> 00:03:36.720
I saw him sitting in a chair on his platform, and the glory of the Lord was tangible in the atmosphere of the church.

00:03:38.440 --> 00:03:46.319
He was like a big papa bear watching over the flock as the shepherd of that church.

00:03:53.428 --> 00:03:59.451
The glory of the Lord was tangible.

00:04:01.280 --> 00:04:11.040
Do you remember I told you mist would show up in services and, as it dissipates, it would leave gold dust on people's skin?

00:04:11.040 --> 00:04:24.959
That's what I saw coming even in his church—a mist of the glory where the residue of the glory of the Lord would leave a type of gold dust.

00:04:25.279 --> 00:04:40.720
I know there has been mockery of this, like people trying to fake it, but the Lord said to me, 'Brandon, there's going to be an authentic move of this that won't be mocked, fake, or man-made.

00:04:40.720 --> 00:04:52.450
' This is going to be a tangible visitation of the Lord that nobody's going to be able to duplicate other than Jesus.

00:05:00.373 --> 00:05:05.646
I saw that at that church and I saw everybody getting healed.

00:05:05.646 --> 00:05:08.960
I saw the glory of the Lord.

00:05:11.223 --> 00:05:20.400
I know he's probably getting older, but the Lord said, 'I'm about to give him a second wind, a new wind of my glory, a new wind of my presence upon his church.

00:05:20.400 --> 00:05:25.493
' What happened at Pensacola and the Brownsville Revival will be times ten.

00:05:29.820 --> 00:05:37.394
I thought that was a very interesting number when the Lord said that to me because usually, the Lord deals in double for the trouble or sevenfold or a hundredfold.

00:05:53.460 --> 00:05:53.800
He said times ten.

00:05:55.500 --> 00:06:06.139
The weightiness of the Brownsville Revival would be times ten in what's about to happen at the Church of His Presence there in Daphne, Alabama.

00:06:16.000 --> 00:06:19.520
All glory to Jesus; I'm excited for that congregation.

00:06:19.839 --> 00:06:21.960
Then He showed me Perry Stone.

00:06:24.000 --> 00:06:33.008
In the vision, the Lord showed me John Kilpatrick by himself, but Perry had someone standing beside him, a younger person helping him.

00:06:33.008 --> 00:06:38.920
This would be around the clock, 24 hours a day.

00:06:55.200 --> 00:06:55.520
I'm talking about glorious church services that you just don't want to unhook from.

00:06:55.520 --> 00:07:01.028
Brother Hagin used to say all the time that sometimes you just have to unhook from a service.

00:07:05.143 --> 00:07:08.720
But what I saw coming were services that you just don't unhook from until you feel it lift.

00:07:08.720 --> 00:07:11.750
God's about to show up and show off in people's lives.

00:07:14.540 --> 00:07:14.730
I saw massive silos again.

00:07:14.730 --> 00:07:22.440
When I went to heaven before, the Lord allowed me to see the silos with the body parts—eyes, ears, people that needed creative miracles.

00:07:22.440 --> 00:07:29.600
Those silos were full of parts, and the Lord said, 'I'm emptying my silos, Brandon.

00:07:29.600 --> 00:07:38.275
There's no need for them up here for what I'm about to do.

00:07:38.275 --> 00:07:47.280
' This will be the greatest grace explosion, for it's the goodness of God that brings man to repentance.

00:07:47.280 --> 00:07:53.787
Goodness and mercy are about to show up and show off in your life.

00:07:53.787 --> 00:08:03.587
I saw waves, and these waves were full of body parts—whatever you needed: kidneys, hearts, lungs, a spleen, a pancreas, or livers.

00:08:03.587 --> 00:08:07.531
I don't want to call them body parts.

00:08:09.660 --> 00:08:09.870
A body part is not an organ.

00:08:09.870 --> 00:08:22.144
I guess a body part is like a finger, or hand, or whatever, but these were organs—like what you need to sustain life, what you have to have.

00:08:22.144 --> 00:08:24.263
They were inside of these waves.

00:08:37.600 --> 00:08:38.000
And as the wave would crash into the church, into the revival, there was another wave.

00:08:53.360 --> 00:08:53.600
You know how sometimes when you see a massive wave on the beach, it takes a little bit of time for the wave to come back?

00:08:58.160 --> 00:08:58.520
These waves were right upon each other.

00:08:58.520 --> 00:09:05.413
That's why he started saying, 'The glory, the glory, the glory.

00:09:05.413 --> 00:09:16.180
' Every time I said 'the glory,' those were waves crashing in and bringing the supply, bringing whatever you needed.

00:09:16.180 --> 00:09:18.764
And he said, 'Receive it as a child.

00:09:18.764 --> 00:09:20.175
' Remember what he said?

00:09:20.175 --> 00:09:24.959
He said, 'It's time for you to receive it as a child.

00:09:24.959 --> 00:09:26.640
Don't come as spiritual adults.

00:09:26.640 --> 00:09:35.405
Come as little children unto the Father,' because he said that's the kind of faith it takes.

00:09:35.405 --> 00:09:44.720
It's like whenever you tell your little child, 'Honey, we're going to go to the store,' they just trust.

00:09:44.720 --> 00:09:45.360
They just believe it.

00:09:45.360 --> 00:09:48.040
There's no doubt; doubt is taught.

00:09:55.700 --> 00:09:55.970
The Lord said it's because of mistrust.

00:10:10.507 --> 00:10:16.667
You might disappoint them, and they have a seed of mistrust because of you not fulfilling what you said.

00:10:16.667 --> 00:10:20.408
But God is a God that doesn't come up short.

00:10:20.408 --> 00:10:26.196
His hand is always full and ready to give unto his children.

00:10:26.711 --> 00:10:30.320
The Lord said, 'Come to me as little children.

00:10:30.320 --> 00:10:33.980
' I saw the wave of God's glory and I saw great finances.

00:10:43.977 --> 00:10:44.229
And he said, 'Do you see that money?

00:10:44.229 --> 00:10:47.792
' I said, 'Yeah, I can see it.

00:10:47.792 --> 00:10:53.400
' But a lot of times when he's talking, I don't tell everything.

00:10:53.400 --> 00:10:57.249
I'm here and I'm seeing—it's all so real.

00:10:57.249 --> 00:11:00.080
Everything is what the Lord is showing me.

00:11:04.000 --> 00:11:04.240
I saw gold coins.

00:11:08.730 --> 00:11:09.176
I saw things that the Lord showed me.

00:11:09.176 --> 00:11:11.189
Brandon, this is the outpouring of finances.

00:11:11.189 --> 00:11:16.959
As I prayed tonight, we were seeing the glory and the tangible presence of the Lord in these services.

00:11:16.959 --> 00:11:20.471
It was for the youth; it was for the people.

00:11:20.471 --> 00:11:25.406
He said, 'I told you there has to be a foundation of wealth, a wealth transfer.

00:11:25.406 --> 00:11:38.675
' People go, 'I don't like talking about it because I'm going to talk more about the blood of Jesus, I'm going to talk more about the healing power of God.

00:11:38.675 --> 00:11:53.943
' But there's a part of it because there's been such a bad taste in a lot of the body of Christ, especially in the charismatic circles, about finances because of things a lot of preachers focused on in the past.

00:11:54.194 --> 00:11:57.261
The Lord said, 'Listen, there's a new wave of glory.

00:11:57.519 --> 00:12:01.980
There's a new wave of my finances for a remnant of one percent.

00:12:01.980 --> 00:12:03.376
' Do you understand?

00:12:15.783 --> 00:12:18.360
It won't be everybody because he can't trust everybody with it.

00:12:18.360 --> 00:12:21.600
If he can't get it through you, he won't get it to you.

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:27.440
And the Lord said to me, 'I'm going to bless those that will help with this end-time harvest.

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:31.291
There's going to be a great outpouring for the end-time harvest, Brandon.

00:12:31.291 --> 00:12:37.897
' And that's what he was talking to me about, because I said, 'Lord, tonight, I'm disappointed inside.

00:12:37.897 --> 00:12:44.409
' Not 'boy,' but inside of me, I'm disappointed inside for how I've seen crypto beaten this last week.

00:12:44.409 --> 00:12:49.990
And I was like, 'Man, it's kind of a bummer that it's crashed on me.

00:12:49.990 --> 00:12:53.387
' He said, 'I told you: great shakeouts and great fake outs, Brandon.

00:12:53.387 --> 00:12:55.417
What part did you not understand?

00:12:55.417 --> 00:12:57.200
' I said, 'Yeah, you did, Lord.

00:12:57.200 --> 00:12:59.726
' This is all just my opinion of what the Lord told me.

00:12:59.726 --> 00:13:00.731
That's not financial advice.

00:13:00.731 --> 00:13:07.360
I'm not here to give you financial advice on what I feel in my heart or what the Lord is telling me.

00:13:07.360 --> 00:13:09.177
You need to hear the Holy Ghost for yourself.

00:13:09.177 --> 00:13:13.680
And if the Lord tells you anything, you go with what he tells you.

00:13:13.680 --> 00:13:15.956
Whatever he tells you to do, do it.

00:13:16.240 --> 00:13:20.280
He's not going to tell every single one of us to do the exact same thing, so I have to make that clear.

00:13:20.280 --> 00:13:24.742
I am not advising you financially because, you know what?

00:13:24.742 --> 00:13:25.839
I'm just human.

00:13:26.586 --> 00:13:28.827
I could be way flat wrong.

00:13:29.200 --> 00:13:33.333
So, it's very dangerous talking about it, but I'm telling you what I've been praying about.

00:13:33.564 --> 00:13:37.960
You have to be a mature adult and sit and listen.

00:13:39.040 --> 00:13:42.267
As I was praying, I've been praying about those four doors.

00:13:43.213 --> 00:13:52.377
And everybody knows, if you've been praying with me, it's not the last video, but the Sunday before, whenever the Lord showed me the doors.

00:13:53.154 --> 00:13:59.120
I've been praying over them, but every single time he always talks to me about Eric and Don Jr.

00:13:59.120 --> 00:14:00.125
'Watch them.

00:14:00.125 --> 00:14:00.628
Watch them.

00:14:00.628 --> 00:14:02.959
' I said, 'Why?

00:14:02.959 --> 00:14:04.240
' Because you'll learn something.

00:14:04.560 --> 00:14:08.560
He said, 'You'll learn something, son, from people who have it.

00:14:08.560 --> 00:14:11.299
Don't you want to learn from the people who have it?

00:14:11.299 --> 00:14:17.871
You don't learn prosperity from poverty; you learn prosperity from prosperity.

00:14:18.959 --> 00:14:19.554
It's taught.

00:14:19.554 --> 00:14:32.480
' If you've never been around money before and your family's always been dead broke and you go from paycheck to paycheck, you don't ask financial advice from people who barely make it financially.

00:14:32.480 --> 00:14:34.160
That's stupid.

00:14:34.160 --> 00:14:38.880
You look at people who have billions in the bank and you go, 'How'd they get it?

00:14:38.880 --> 00:14:39.876
Is it all legal?

00:14:39.876 --> 00:14:41.888
' I don't know; it's not my place to judge.

00:14:41.888 --> 00:14:56.440
But I look at it and say, 'When the Lord says pay attention, for I'm going to restore the finances of the Trumps for everything they lost trying to be obedient to what I asked them to do.

00:14:56.440 --> 00:15:01.760
' Donald, I'm going to restore back the fountain of wealth to that family.

00:15:01.760 --> 00:15:14.343
I'm going to restore what the cankerworm ate over the last four and a half or five years—the persecution that they received in New York and the businesses and the business dealings, the money that they lost.

00:15:14.343 --> 00:15:24.331
The Lord said, 'I'm going to restore it back by three, and their wealth will multiply during his term by three, and it may even multiply by more.

00:15:24.331 --> 00:15:24.982
' I don't know.

00:15:24.982 --> 00:15:26.160
I'm believing God for them.

00:15:26.640 --> 00:15:28.560
Why not?

00:15:28.560 --> 00:15:32.480
It takes a lot of pressure, and they've been through a lot as a family.

00:15:32.628 --> 00:15:34.719
You say, 'Well, boohoo, they're billionaires.

00:15:34.719 --> 00:15:35.793
' You know what?

00:15:35.793 --> 00:15:42.840
If you lost billions of dollars and you lost it all, I'm not going to go down that road.

00:15:44.240 --> 00:15:46.580
So, the Lord said, 'Watch them.

00:15:46.580 --> 00:15:51.893
' As I've been watching them, this is what he said today.

00:15:56.365 --> 00:15:56.628
Did you see his little tweet, his little post, and all his stuff?

00:16:09.040 --> 00:16:09.370
It's all over the news today.

00:16:09.370 --> 00:16:12.250
Did anybody see what Eric Trump said today?

00:16:16.867 --> 00:16:17.413
I thought this was an interesting recent comment.

00:16:17.413 --> 00:16:19.853
Can they see it?

00:16:19.853 --> 00:16:20.360
Yeah.

00:16:26.000 --> 00:16:28.000
And I thought, 'Well, that's interesting.

00:16:28.000 --> 00:16:31.706
It's falling like a rock this week.

00:16:31.706 --> 00:16:36.133
' And he said, 'This is the greatest time to buy.

00:16:36.133 --> 00:16:44.976
' All his little articles are saying this and that.

00:16:51.804 --> 00:16:52.169
And I thought, 'Well, that's interesting.

00:16:52.169 --> 00:17:01.774
' That's interesting because the Lord told us even in the last video to watch the Trumps, and I thought that was kind of interesting.

00:17:06.426 --> 00:17:06.799
I'm just saying you learn from people who have it.

00:17:11.097 --> 00:17:11.554
I wouldn't learn from Nancy for what I've seen about that.

00:17:11.554 --> 00:17:15.839
But I just want to give all glory to Jesus.

00:17:15.839 --> 00:17:16.461
Isn't he wonderful, y'all?

00:17:16.461 --> 00:17:18.459
Because he's trying to prepare us for something.

00:17:18.459 --> 00:17:29.440
As I was praying, even when I went to church tonight and we had our prayer group, I sat and listened.

00:17:29.440 --> 00:17:34.080
And he said, 'Brandon, you're not believing for big enough.

00:17:34.080 --> 00:17:38.743
' I said, 'Lord, I'm believing for millions.

00:17:38.743 --> 00:17:40.978
' He said, 'You're not believing big enough.

00:17:40.978 --> 00:17:42.411
' I said, 'Lord, really?

00:17:44.773 --> 00:17:45.147
I stretched myself.

00:17:45.147 --> 00:17:50.420
What do you want me to believe for?

00:17:50.420 --> 00:17:57.669
' He said, 'I am believing for what I need for the billion-soul harvest.

00:17:57.669 --> 00:18:01.262
You don't have a clue what that means.

00:18:07.884 --> 00:18:08.160
A million dollars isn't going to get it.

00:18:08.160 --> 00:18:12.500
Two million isn't going to get it, Brandon.

00:18:12.500 --> 00:18:14.920
' I said, 'What about ten million?

00:18:14.920 --> 00:18:18.060
' He said, "That’s not enough either.

00:18:18.060 --> 00:18:21.794
" I said, "$10 million ain’t enough?

00:18:21.794 --> 00:18:25.600
" I said, "Lord, $10 million?

00:18:25.600 --> 00:18:29.680
That’s a lot of money.

00:18:48.430 --> 00:18:48.760
" He said, "No.

00:18:51.771 --> 00:18:54.799
" He said, "Brandon, you need to believe for hundreds of millions.

00:18:54.799 --> 00:18:58.467
" I said, "Believe for hundreds of millions of dollars.

00:19:19.822 --> 00:19:20.231
" I said, "Lord, my capacity—you’ve got to stretch me.

00:19:20.231 --> 00:19:22.880
" He said, "Think bigger.

00:19:22.880 --> 00:19:26.971
You’ve got to think bigger.

00:19:26.971 --> 00:19:33.299
It’s going to take a lot to bring in this harvest: the churches, the finances to bring all this in.

00:19:33.299 --> 00:19:38.112
" We get excited when a hundred people get born again—I do.

00:19:38.112 --> 00:19:46.400
We have a hundred people get born again and it’s pretty much free.

00:19:46.400 --> 00:19:48.840
You know, YouTube—thank God for it.

00:19:48.840 --> 00:19:53.280
But the Lord said, "Brandon, there are billions of people dying and going to hell.

00:19:53.280 --> 00:20:00.480
Over 170,000 people die every single day, and a great percentage of them do not know me.

00:20:00.480 --> 00:20:10.792
But you’re excited about the hundred while 170,000 died today, and a large percentage of them went to hell.

00:20:10.792 --> 00:20:11.200
" And the Lord is always stretching me.

00:20:11.200 --> 00:20:12.250
He’s always thinking.

00:20:11.200 --> 00:20:11.227
He makes me think bigger.

00:20:11.227 --> 00:20:11.254
And I go, "Okay.

00:20:11.254 --> 00:20:11.395
" In my mind, I go, "Thanks for the hundred, Lord.

00:20:11.395 --> 00:20:11.440
Thanks for the hundred souls.

00:20:11.440 --> 00:20:13.190
" And we’re excited about them.

00:20:11.440 --> 00:20:11.505
But he said, "Enlarge your capacity to believe me for more.

00:20:11.505 --> 00:20:11.600
You must believe for the biggest harvest of souls this world has ever seen.

00:20:15.343 --> 00:20:15.615
You must believe for this.

00:20:15.615 --> 00:20:22.149
" So as he says that to me, I stretch because this revival—what’s about to take place—is going to take great finances.

00:20:22.149 --> 00:20:40.928
I’m telling you folks, people get all bent up out of shape about things, but I’m trying to tell you where he’s at and what he’s dealing with me about.

00:20:40.928 --> 00:20:42.303
Stretch.

00:20:42.303 --> 00:20:45.430
Get beyond poverty thinking, son.

00:20:45.430 --> 00:20:48.799
Get beyond poverty thinking.

00:21:15.360 --> 00:21:32.982
And I say, "Well, Lord, I don’t like the way the whole prosperity gospel and all the stuff was going on about it.

00:21:45.040 --> 00:21:45.600
I don’t like all the stuff.

00:21:47.577 --> 00:21:49.063
" He said, "Don’t talk against it.

00:21:49.063 --> 00:21:50.480
Don’t run them down.

00:21:53.679 --> 00:21:54.022
Just know.

00:21:54.022 --> 00:21:58.137
Don’t learn from what they did and perfect it.

00:21:58.137 --> 00:22:02.907
I’ll do more with you if you just keep your heart right.

00:22:02.907 --> 00:22:04.907
Believe me.

00:22:04.907 --> 00:22:07.429
" But I said, "Lord, what do you want me to do?

00:22:07.429 --> 00:22:09.142
" I’m always asking, "What do you want me to do, Lord?

00:22:09.142 --> 00:22:13.440
" But he was talking to me about crypto again.

00:22:17.235 --> 00:22:22.400
And he said, "I told you that it would be a new industrial revolution.

00:22:22.400 --> 00:22:24.959
A foundation has to be laid.

00:22:28.587 --> 00:22:31.747
And there is much foundation that needs to be laid, for it is the wild, wild west.

00:22:34.098 --> 00:22:34.355
And it is too volatile.

00:22:36.879 --> 00:22:40.914
And I will bring in legislation that will bring a foundation for stability in the markets in the days ahead.

00:22:40.914 --> 00:22:45.120
Watch 2026, the first quarter.

00:22:45.120 --> 00:22:54.799
Pray over this first quarter for legislation in the Senate to be passed to bring stability and regulations so that it’s not so volatile.

00:22:54.799 --> 00:22:55.828
Watch the Trump administration.

00:22:56.684 --> 00:23:07.156
" And the Lord said, "Pray for them for what will be a new industrial revolution like it was at the beginning when Benjamin Franklin found electricity.

00:23:11.809 --> 00:23:12.059
It will be the Ai, capital A, lowercase i.

